# Accessibility and SEO Guidelines

## Accessibility Standards

### Semantic HTML Structure
```liquid
<!-- Use proper heading hierarchy -->
<main id="MainContent" role="main">
  <header>
    <h1>{{ page_title | default: shop.name }}</h1>
  </header>
  
  <section aria-labelledby="section-heading">
    <h2 id="section-heading">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
    <!-- section content -->
  </section>
  
  <nav aria-label="Main navigation">
    <ul role="menubar">
      <li role="none">
        <a href="/collections" role="menuitem">Collections</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</main>
```

### Skip Links and Navigation
```liquid
<!-- Skip to content link -->
<a class="skip-to-content-link button visually-hidden" href="#MainContent">
  {{ "accessibility.skip_to_text" | t }}
</a>

<!-- Focus management -->
<script>
  document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
    if (e.key === 'Tab') {
      document.body.classList.add('keyboard-navigation');
    }
  });
  
  document.addEventListener('mousedown', function() {
    document.body.classList.remove('keyboard-navigation');
  });
</script>
```

### Image Accessibility
```liquid
{% liquid
  assign alt_text = image.alt | default: section.settings.title
  assign decorative_image = section.settings.decorative_image | default: false
%}

{% if decorative_image %}
  <img src="{{ image | img_url: '800x600' }}" alt="" role="presentation">
{% else %}
  <img src="{{ image | img_url: '800x600' }}" 
       alt="{{ alt_text }}"
       loading="lazy">
{% endif %}
```

### Form Accessibility
```liquid
<form class="contact-form" novalidate>
  <div class="field">
    <label for="contact-name">
      {{ 'contact.form.name' | t }}
      <span class="required" aria-label="required">*</span>
    </label>
    <input type="text" 
           id="contact-name" 
           name="contact[name]" 
           required
           aria-describedby="name-error"
           aria-invalid="false">
    <div id="name-error" class="field-error" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></div>
  </div>
  
  <button type="submit" class="button">
    {{ 'contact.form.send' | t }}
  </button>
</form>
```

### Interactive Elements
```liquid
<!-- Button with proper ARIA attributes -->
<button type="button" 
        class="slider-button" 
        aria-label="Previous slide"
        aria-controls="slider-content"
        disabled>
  <span class="visually-hidden">Previous slide</span>
  {% render 'icon-arrow-left' %}
</button>

<!-- Toggle button -->
<button type="button" 
        class="accordion-toggle" 
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="accordion-content-{{ block.id }}">
  {{ block.settings.title }}
  <span class="accordion-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
</button>
```

### Screen Reader Support
```liquid
<!-- Visually hidden but accessible -->
<span class="visually-hidden">
  {{ 'products.product.price.regular_price' | t }}
</span>
<span class="price">{{ product.price | money }}</span>

<!-- Live regions for dynamic content -->
<div id="cart-count" 
