### Loading States
```liquid
<!-- Loading indicators -->
<div class="product-grid" aria-live="polite">
  <div class="loading-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="visually-hidden">{{ 'general.accessibility.loading' | t }}</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Skeleton loading -->
<div class="skeleton-product-card" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="skeleton-image"></div>
  <div class="skeleton-title"></div>
  <div class="skeleton-price"></div>
</div>
```

### Error Handling
```liquid
<!-- Error messages with proper ARIA -->
<div class="error-message" role="alert" aria-live="assertive">
  <h3>{{ 'general.accessibility.error' | t }}</h3>
  <p>{{ error_message }}</p>
  <button type="button" class="error-dismiss" aria-label="Dismiss error">
    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
  </button>
</div>
```

## Testing and Validation

### Accessibility Testing
- Use screen readers (NVDA, JAWS, VoiceOver)
- Test keyboard navigation (Tab, Enter, Space, Arrow keys)
- Validate with WAVE, axe, or Lighthouse accessibility audits
- Test with high contrast mode and zoom up to 200%

### SEO Testing
- Validate structured data with Google's Rich Results Test
- Check meta tags with SEO browser extensions
- Test mobile-friendliness with Google's Mobile-Friendly Test
- Monitor Core Web Vitals and PageSpeed Insights

